borough: London Borough of Barking and Dagenham
description:
Full Planning Application for the demolition of
existing buildings and structures, and the erection of buildings ranging from 2
storeys to 15 storeys to accommodate 233 residential units and 271 sqm
non-residential floorspace (Use Class E). The proposals include the delivery of
landscaping and public realm, play space, access, car parking and other
associated and ancillary works. [Revised description]
